Package: llmx
Title: LLM-Powered SDMX Data Transformation and Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", , "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for transforming diverse data sources (CSV, Excel, etc.) 
    into SDMX-CSV format using Large Language Models (LLMs). Features include advanced 
    mapping inference with fuzzy matching, workflow orchestration, multiple LLM provider 
    support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama, Azure OpenAI), sophisticated data profiling, 
    and intelligent value transformation suggestions for statistical data exchange workflows.
